Features of this app:
-Offline maps for all over the world
 -Totally free brought to you by NOKIA's HERE maps
 -Different speeches available to download (male female) in various languages 
 -Much Better than GOOGLE MAPS

Instructions (Read Carefully):
 *Download 2 files (1 .rar and 1 .apk files) and download Zarchiver(https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ru.zdevs.zarchiver) from play store
 *Extract .rar file by using app Zarchiver (which one you just downloaded) to the path /sdcard/android/data/
 *Install the given apk file. Turn on GPS and make sure you have working internet connection (1st time you need to run it ONLINE)
 *Sign in to your NOKIA ACCOUNT (this is necessary if you want to use offline maps if you dont have account then create it by pressing SIGN UP button)
 *After signing in swipe left2right and click DOWNLOAD MAPS and then click DOWNLOAD NEW at the bottom select ASIA and then INDIA and then click on the top which has INDIA WHOLE AREA written in it and press DOWNLOAD ICON which is located at right
 *Now if you have followed the steps correctly then app will verify downloaded data and gives you full offline maps (download icon with turn into TRASH icon which means you just got success)
 *Now tick USE APP OFFLINE and enjoy
 *Like US on FB ,Follow on Twitter & Google+
